item.title: SoftLayer_Container_Authentication_Response_AccountIdMissing
item.description: SoftLayer_Container_Authentication_Response_AccountIdMissing Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Container_Authentication_Response_AccountIdMissing data type contains information for specific responses from the getPortalLogin API. This class is indicative of a request that is missing the account id. Local accounts The list of linked accounts for the authenticated SoftLayer customer portal user. Type: SoftLayer_Container_Authentication_Response_Account[] statusKeyName Type: string
